{"title":"书记跟班","authors":["刘志忠"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记跟班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰州化学工业公司工人  刘志忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁一马当先走在前面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象春风过岭，声音这般动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心弦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁急促的脚步嚓嚓响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少难关，脚下踩得稀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烂？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，是书记下来跟班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来战斗的意志、火样的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临阵指挥生产呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和咱工人并肩作战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他满面红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听他铿锵语言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“对，该这样干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们要的，就是高线生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵呵，是书记的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是革命的号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是颗颗红心双双巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧动革命的春潮滚滚……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}